# This .envrc file activates the Nix development environment defined in flake.nix
# When you enter this directory, direnv will automatically load the environment
# When you leave, it will unload it

# Use the Nix flake in this directory
use flake

# Optional: Set project-specific environment variables
# export PROJECT_NAME="my-awesome-project"
# export API_URL="http://localhost:3000"

# Optional: Add project-specific PATH entries
# PATH_add ./node_modules/.bin
# PATH_add ./scripts

# Note: direnv is configured in your Home Manager base profile
# This .envrc file works with that configuration to create a seamless
# development experience that combines:
# 1. Your base profile (essential tools)
# 2. Your personal profile (preferences)
# 3. This project's specific environment
